      <h2>About Wonta Rural Development Association</h2>

      <p>
        Wonta Rural Development Association is committed to empowering rural communities by creating sustainable 
        development programs that improve education, healthcare, agriculture, and economic opportunities.
      </p>

      <p>
        We work hand-in-hand with local leaders and families to understand their needs and build solutions that bring 
        long-term, meaningful change to underserved communities.
      </p>

